{"tid":1034470,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"老細好難頂，應唔應該走，求意見","createTime":"2019-02-24T02:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T11:34:15.000Z","uid":111179,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"33f867647122d0201c4dc292130c4879ae39b1ce","tid":1034470,"uid":111179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T02:53:36.000Z","msg":"2018 fresh grad,做過2份工，第一份求奇搵做住先，做左2個月有一間大公司offer，人工又高d，所以走左<br />\n但而加做左新公司2個月，發現公司好political，老闆又成日搬龍門，例如琴日第一次做某project，用common sense做，d無用既point無放上report，佢就話我無將所有points放上report，之後照佢要求做，佢又會話點解呢d一睇就知無用既point都放上去，再串我話都係比返d straight forward既野你做。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，同旁邊一樣department 但唔同team既同事熟d，傾多d計，一齊食飯，就會話better focus on your work(佢真係咁打)<br />\n<br />\n問題係，我知另一department 請人，應唔應該去同個個team leader傾下推薦下自己，但身分有d尷尬，定係辭職？<br />\n<br />\n求意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07725bc506213572c81b4fe32bf90b736a7d6a37","tid":1034470,"uid":53194,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T03:13:58.000Z","msg":"老細對你印象應該唔係幾好，再繼續都唔會有改善"},{"pid":"877e7d200a07d85192f358ba13af7b97e4b0eeed","tid":1034470,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T03:15:41.000Z","msg":"會唔會你真係有啲on9?"},{"pid":"a60e17da5ad382f8fcd8814408a79ce938d7cbbb","tid":1034470,"uid":57636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T03:17:47.000Z","msg":"要遇到好老闆好難，無咩邊d老細唔西<br />\n𨳒佢老母，闔家剷<br />\n重有嘢學未留低囉<br />\n<br />\n你老細唔係睇曬兩個department?<br />\n想逃避你老細就唔好週調啦<br />\n咁西你都頂到，無咩搞唔掂嘅<br />\n<br />\n得閒留意下行情，睇下重有咩好路數啦"},{"pid":"5d1a35e58c6fae451a65ef3cb347c65cecc0fe3f","tid":1034470,"uid":111179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"877e7d200a07d85192f358ba13af7b97e4b0eeed","tid":1034470,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"reply